  "title": "Deliciously Snappy Ethiopian Lentils Skillet",
  "description": "A fermented and snappy Ethiopian dish featuring chocolate chips, perfect for a brunch mood, this plant-based friendly recipe is a unique twist on traditional Ethiopian cuisine.",
